textBeforeTable: The costs of collecting and disposing of discarded materials either through deposit in a landfill and/or incineration. It also includes landfill tipping fees, incineration fees, trash collection and hauling services, as well as internal fees charged by the waste innovation program. If recycling costs are included on the same invoice, for convenience include them in this expense account. If invoices are only for recycling, use Recycling Services 533020 instead.
